---
name: Marine Forecast Ingest
version: "1.0"
globs: ["**/*forecast*.{ts,js,py}", "lib/**/*", "server/**/*"]
triggers: [file_change]
---
- Inputs: {time, wave_m, wind_kt, vis_km, period_s} (UTC 정규화)
- Must: schema validate(json-schema), NaN/누락 fail-fast
- Tests: 단위 변환(kt↔m/s), 리샘플링, 누락열, 경계시간 포함성
- Disallow: silent coercion / implicit provider fallback
